<h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Help users to get to an answer</h1>
<div class="govuk-body">
  <p>Guide users to relevant information they need using a questionnaire.</p>

  <p>Based on their situation, this can help users understand:</p>
  
  <ul>
    <li>what they can get</li>
    <li>which actions to take</li>
  </ul>
  
  <p>You can add this questionnaire to an existing service or campaign website. </p>
</div>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Before you start</h2>

<div class="govuk-body">
  <p>Read about <a href="#">'Get to an answer' on the DfE Design Manual</a> to help decide if this pattern is right for your use case. </p>

  <p>You do not need to request permission to use this but you will need to follow your team’s processes for reviewing and publishing content. </p>

  <p>You can sign in using your DfE Microsoft account. </p>
</div>

